Decompress "elks.tar" in /root. Eg:
# cd /root
# mount /dev/fd1 /mnt
# tar xvf /mnt/elks-0.2.tar

And after, source the "setenv.sh"
# . setenv.sh

To test the toolchain, go to "examples" directory and type:
# make -f Makefile.elks all

After some time, three binaries should be produced: test, chess and show_fonts. Try them!
: )

19/12/2024 - Rafael Diniz
